      <article class="blog-post">
        <h1 class="blog-post__title">The Basilisks NFT</h1>
        <p class="blog-post__category"><strong>Gaming</strong></p>
        <p class="blog-post__author">Tony Nguyen</p>
        <p class="blog-post__date">20 Jun 2022</p>

        <p class="blog-post__text">
          The Basilisks that <strong>players</strong> collect are represented with
          NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain with real-world value. Players use
          <strong>the Basilisks they have</strong> gathered to battle other players
          to win ether (ETH).
        </p>

        <p class="blog-post__text">
          In Balthazar Dragons, players are immersed in a 3D open world to explore
          and capture dragon-like beasts called Basilisks. Balthazar Dragons is an
          upcoming fantasy role-playing game developed on the Ethereum blockchain by
          a decentralized autonomous organization (DAO) called the Balthazar DAO.
        </p>

        <ul class="blog-post__list">
          <li class="blog-post__list-item">List name 1</li>
          <li class="blog-post__list-item">List name 2</li>
