          <li class="blog-post__list-item">List name 4</li>
        </ul>

        <blockquote class="blog-post__quote">
          "The first huge metaverse arena to arrange live sports, hang out, and even
          make bets and wagers."
        </blockquote>

        <p class="blog-post__rating"><strong>8.5/10 Markout Corporation</strong></p>

